@startuml
header Student Contact Lifecycle
state "Active Student" as Active
state "Archived Student" as Archived
state "Deleted" as Deleted <<low>>

[*] --> Active : add n/Student...

Active --> Archived : archive [index]
note on link
  Student is hidden
  from main list
end note

Archived --> Active : restore [index]
note on link
  Student returns
  to main list
end note

Active --> Deleted : delete [index]
Archived --> Deleted : delete [index]

Deleted --> [*]
@enduml
